snippet: Last-placed Queens Park Rangers, with the help of Shaun Wright-Phillips, a former Chelsea player, scored its first victory at Chelsea in 30 years.
abstract: Queens Park Rangers, bottom team in English soccer's Premier League, defeat Chelsea, 1-0, their first victory at Chelsea in 30 years.
lead_paragraph: Last-placed Queens Park Rangers, with the help of Shaun Wright-Phillips, a former Chelsea player, scored its first victory at Chelsea in 30 years.

headline.main: Queens Park Earns Rare Victory at Chelsea
headline.print_headline: Chelsea Falls to Queens Park Rangers
